I'm in search of some Illustrations to demonstrate that Unit Testing 
(white box testing with JUnit or practising Test Driven Development)will 
increase the productivity of developers and reduce the Defect density 
and effort spent in Man hours.

with Graphs, Tables ect with real time data will be of immense help.
If any one of you have related materials plz do foward it to me and do 
the needfull.
